#: ../../K/Knuth.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Donald E. Knuth's *The Art of Computer Programming*\\] Mythically, the "
"reference that answers all questions about data structures or algorithms. A "
"safe answer when you do not know: \"I think you can find that in Knuth.\" "
"Contrast :ref:`the-literature`\\. See also :ref:`bible`\\. There is a Donald"
" Knuth home page at `http://Sunburn.Stanford.EDU/~knuth/ "
"<http://Sunburn.Stanford.EDU/~knuth/>`_."
msgstr ""
"[Donald E. Knuthの\\ *The Art of Computer Programming*\\ "
"より]神話的には、データ構造やアルゴリズムに関するあらゆる疑問に答えてくれる参考文献。分からないときの無難な答え:「それはKnuthに載っていると思うよ」。\\"
" :ref:`the-literature`\\ と対比せよ。\\ :ref:`bible`\\ も参照。Donald Knuthのホームページが\\ "
"`http://Sunburn.Stanford.EDU/~knuth/ "
"<http://Sunburn.Stanford.EDU/~knuth/>`_\\ にある。"
